В Одесі вночі згоріли 18 автомобілів 
Три загоряння автомобілів на автостоянках сталися в ніч на вівторок у трьох районах Одеси. 
Як повідомила прес-служба Головного управління Держслужби з надзвичайних ситуацій в Одеській області, близько 3:00 ночі до Служби порятунку "101" надійшло повідомлення про загоряння легкових автомобілів на території житлового масиву "Райдужний". Унаслідок пожежі було знищено три й пошкоджено шість легкових автомобілів. 
О 4.22 пожежникам надійшло повідомлення, що на вул. Базарній у центрі Одеси сталося загоряння автомобілів на вуличній стоянці. Внаслідок пожежі вогонь знищив дві й пошкодив ще дві машини. При цьому пожежникам вдалося врятувати шість легкових автомобілів. 
Ще через півгодини на вул. Рекордній в Одесі виникло загоряння п'яти легкових автомобілів на загальній площі 25 кв. м. Причини займання та збитки з’ясовуються. 
За даними місцевих жителів, чиї машини згоріли або постраждали, в усіх випадках причиною пожеж був підпал. 
Поліція ситуацію поки що не коментує. Події

RAIS  wa Burundi Pierre Nkurunziza, ametoa agizo jipya kuhusu upigaji wa ngoma za matambiko na kupiga marufuku wanawake kupiga ngoma hizo. Pia ameamuru kuwa ngoma hizo za matambiko kupigwa tu katika shughuli maalumu. Katika agizo lake imeelezwa kuwa ni marufuku mwanamke kupiga ngoma hizo za tambiko lakini wanawake wanaruhusiwa kushiriki katika kucheza wakati wakipigiwa ngoma hizo. Kama ilivyo katika nchi nyingi za Kiafrika  ngoma hii ya tambiko siku hizi inachezwa kama burudani, lakini kwa miongo mingi ilikuwa ni ngoma iliyoabudiwa na kabila zima la Kirundi. Katika siku za karibuni ngoma hii imekuwa ikichezwa kwenye maharusi, graduation hata ubatizo. Ngoma hii ambayo awali ilikuwa ikipigwa na wanaume tu, kwa sasa kulianzishwa hata vikundi vya wanawake ambavyo vilianza kupiga ngoma hii. Kwa tamko jipya kila anaetaka kufanya onyesho la ngoma hii atalipia $280, na kama onyesho litafanyika nje ya nchi kiwango hicho kitalipwa kila siku.

posts.text:
Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation Communications and Marketing Officer in Ottawa , Ontario 
CMHC: Because What I Do Matters 
Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation (CMHC) helps Canadians meet their housing needs. As Canada’s authority on housing, we contribute to the stability of the housing market and financial system, provide support for Canadians in housing need, and offer unbiased housing research and advice to Canadian governments, consumers and the housing industry. Prudent risk management, strong corporate governance and transparency are cornerstones of our operations. 
Bring your communication and marketing expertise and your relationship-building skills to this positon in Ottawa. 
This position is an exceptional opportunity to become a member of the Public Affairs team, where you will support the development and implementation of communications and marketing strategies and activities to assist in the achievement of business line goals and/or corporate priorities. Additionally, you will be responsible for supporting the development and maintenance of an integrated channel management strategy, monitoring customer engagement, and coordinating CMHC activities with various internal and external clients. You will be also promoting and ensuring compliance with CMHC's corporate identity and branding style guide, and ensures consistency in messaging. 
How You Will Be Contributing 
Strategy, Planning, and Delivery 
Supporting the development and implementation of communications and marketing strategies and plans in response to business line and/or corporate priorities by researching key issues, trends, developments, attitudes, opinions and likely reactions by principal stakeholders. 
Executing the production of material and the maintenance of appropriate marketing, communications, information products and activities, including pro-active and re-active messages, for employees to fully service their clients; responsible for the life cycle of content. 
Providing advice and functional guidance on requirements of communications and marketing protocols. Liaising cross-functionally to gather intelligence on business line and client needs. 
Research and Analysis 
Analyzing trends and topics in customer engagement with CMHC content/topics, such as inquiries and issues, and ensuring that information provided to customers is clear and complete while reporting issues internally in a timely manner . 
Monitoring the effectiveness of the mechanisms in place and analyzes results to turn information into insights. Generating reports on the usefulness and effectiveness of communications and marketing tools and activities, and making recommendations for improvement. 
Conducting research and analysis in the determination of the best communication approach for all audiences and deliverable methods. 
Quality Assurance 
Providing criteria and direction to ensure compliance with recommendations and best practices for content management. Ensuring consistency in the delivery of CMHC messaging and brand. 
Identifying and bringing forward communications issues to ensure they are addressed from a communications and marketing perspective. 
What We Are Looking For 
A commitment to demonstrating CMHC values. 
University degree in Communications and Marketing, Journalism, or in a related discipline with a minimum of 3 years of relevant work experience; or equivalent qualifications obtained through at least 5 years of success in related positions of increasing responsibility. 
Demonstrated experience in writing and editing communications and marketing plans and a variety of communications and marketing products. 
Demonstrated experience interpreting web and social media analytics. 
Demonstrated experience working with a CRM, marketing automation tools and creating and deploying email marketing campaigns considered an asset. 
Knowledge of current industry trends and technology and a willingness to stay abreast of changes through continuous learning. 
Strong oral and written communication skills including presentation skills. 
Strong client management skills with the ability to build and maintain relationships. 
Demonstrated project management skills. 
Experience coordinating multiple projects and ability to shift priorities on a daily basis. 
Ability to prioritize and to work independently and in a team setting. 
Core Competencies 
Client Focus/ Innovation/ Valuing and Respecting Individuals 
Functional Competencies 
Analytical Thinking/ Coaching and Feedback/ Commitment to Official Languages/Consensus Building/ Flexibility/ Focus on Results/ Forward/Strategic Thinking/ Learning and Growth/ Open-Mindedness/Listening/ Organizational Know-How and Awareness/ Relationship Building/ Teamwork 
What CMHC Has To Offer Competitive Total Compensation package 
o Comprehensive flex benefit program 
o Defined Benefits Pension Plan (effective January 1, 2018) 
o Eligibility for Performance Bonuses 
In-house learning and development opportunities 
Career Growth Opportunities 
Employee and Family Assistance Program (EFAP) 
New Hire Mentorship Program 
Various onsite amenities 
APPLY today 
This job posting will be active until 11:59 pm EST on November 13, 2017 , however, the competition may remain active until a successful candidate has been chosen. 
To Note 
We sincerely thank all candidates for their interest, however, please note that only those applicants selected for further consideration will be contacted. If selected for an interview, please advise us if you require an accommodation. 
Selected candidates may be required to do a presentation or assessment as part of the interview. If so, they will be advised in advance. In the event that tests are administered, candidates will also be advised in advance. 
One of the positions requires bilingualism in English and French, with the ability to read, understand and speak in your second official language at an advanced level, and to write in your second official language at an intermediate level. Candidates who do not currently have valid language test results recognised by CMHC will be required to take a language test. https://www.cmhc-schl.gc.ca/en/corp/ca/upload/guide-second-laguage-proficiency-tests.pdf Candidates must be eligible for Reliability Clearance. 
Candidates who do not meet all of the position requirements may be considered in an under-fill capacity, in which case the person will be hired at a lower level than the position level. 
/ All applications submitted to this competition will be kept for a six (6) month period and may be considered for future related vacancies at CMHC. /

DASH/USD 
DASH continues to go sideways overall, as we are in a relatively well-defined consolidation phase. Ultimately, this is a “buy on the dip” type of market, but you should build a larger position, and show quite a bit of patience as it will be needed. 
LTC/USD

به گزارش مشرق ، باشگاه لاتزیو در تابستان اخیر قصد به خدمت گرفتن سردار آزمون را از روبین‌کازان داشت و حتی گفته شد که این انتقال در ازای 18 میلیون یورو در آستانه عملی شدن است، اما خرید کایسدو توسط لاتزیو، جذب مهاجم ایرانی روبین‌کازان را تحت‌الشعاع خود قرار داد و این قضیه منتفی شد، هر چند در آن موقع هم گفته شد که ماجرای به خدمت گرفتن آزمون تنها به تعویق می‌افتد و لاتزیو در پنجره بعدی نقل‌وانتقالات یعنی ژانویه 2018 مجدداً سراغ گلزن تیم ملی ایران خواهد رفت.

posts.text:
Ducati Panigale V4, svelata ad Eicma la prima 4 cilindri di Borgo Panigale derivata dalla MotoGP di Francesco Irace 1 SPECIALE EICMA INTERESSANTE ALD presenta "2W: due ruote, zero pensieri". L'innovativa proposta di mobilità motociclistica FRIZZANTE Vespa Sprint, aggiornamenti stilistici e tecnici per l'evergreen scooter di Piaggio EICMA Eicma, Ministro Madia e Pres. Confindustria Boccia inaugurano la 75/ma edizione. Keanu Reeves, Agostini, Biaggi, e Cairoli testimonial MILANO - Come preannunciato nei mesi scorsi, Ducati svela a Eicma 2017 la nuova Panigale V4, prima moto del marchio bolognese ad essere equipaggiata con un motore quattro cilindri strettamente derivato da quello utilizzato in MotoGP.
La nuova Panigale V4 andrà a sostituire la 1299, da cui eredita gran parte del design pur essendo dotata di alcuni dettagli ancora più aggressivi, soprattutto nella parte frontale. Il cuore, vero e proprio elemento di spicco della nuova moto, è un quattro cilindri a V da 1.103 cc capace di sviluppare ben 214 cv a 13.000 giri/min esprimendo un rapporto peso/potenza di 1,1 cv/kg. Tuttavia attingendo dal catalogo accessori e montando lo scarico che Akrapovic ha realizzato su specifiche del reparto Ducati Corse, la potenza della V4 Panigale può arrivare fino a 226 cv.
Sarà proposta sul mercato anche in una versione S, equipaggiata con raffinate sospensioni Ohlins con sistema Smart EC 2.0 e componentistica di altissimo livello come le ruote forgiate in alluminio e la batteria agli ioni di litio, e nella variante Speciale, realizzata in serie limitata con una livrea dedicata, cerchi forgiati in magnesio e scarico in titanio.
Il maggior (inevitabile) peso della moto è stato compensato dalla presenza di un nuovo telaio perimetrale “Front Frame” più compatto e leggero, che sfrutta proprio il motore come elemento portante. Anche l'elettronica, infine, che beneficia del know how acquisito dall'azienda nelle corse, rappresenta il massimo che si può chiedere oggi da una moto sportiva. La piattaforma inerziale a sei assi di Bosch rappresenta un vero e proprio cervello realizzato per rendere la moto più performante e più sicura allo stesso tempo. Spiccano, tra i tanti sistemi, l'ABS cornering con controlli inediti per gestire la derapat e il QuickShift up & down.

No one can deny the fact that a person's education is the most important aspect of his life. 没有人能否人这一事实：教育是人生最重要的一方面。
People equate success in life with the ability of operating computer. 人们把会使用计算机与人生成功相提并论。
According to a recent survey, four-million people die each year from diseases linked to smoking. 依照最近的一项调查，每年有4,000,000人死于与吸烟相关的疾病。
The latest surveys show that quiet a few children have unpleasant associations with homework. 最近的调查显示相当多的孩子对家庭作业没什么好感。
No invention has received more praise and abuse than Internet. 没有一项发明像互联网那样同时受到如此多的赞扬和批评。

thread.title_full: 年間7万人を超える大学中退者を減少させる策を提案 業界初サービス【大学中退相談コンシェルジュ（仮称）】 “気軽に相談できる”機会を提供 2018年春より開始

posts.author: 株式会社ジェイック
posts.title: 年間7万人を超える大学中退者を減少させる策を提案 業界初サービス【大学中退相談コンシェルジュ（仮称）】 “気軽に相談できる”機会を提供 2018年春より開始
posts.text:
ツイート 
就職支援事業を展開する株式会社ジェイック（所在地：東京都千代田区、代表取締役：佐藤 剛志、以下「ジェイック」）と、特定非営利活動法人NEWVERY（所在地：東京都品川区、理事長：小崎 文恵、以下「NEWVERY」）は、大学在学中に中退に関する相談ができる業界初のチャットサービス「大学中退相談コンシェルジュ（仮称）」を、2018年春より共同で開始します。 就職支援事業を展開する株式会社ジェイック（所在地：東京都千代田区、代表取締役：佐藤 剛志、以下「ジェイック」）と、特定非営利活動法人NEWVERY（所在地：東京都品川区、理事長：小崎 文恵、以下「NEWVERY」）は、2017年11月7日の【中退してしまった学生の実態から迫る中退予防の方向性】講演会内で、大学在学中に中退に関する相談ができる業界初のチャットサービス「大学中退相談コンシェルジュ（仮称）」を、2018年春より共同で開始することを発表しました。「大学中退相談コンシェルジュ（仮称）」とは、大学・大学院中退を迷っている学生を対象に、チャット機能を通じて専門相談員に対して相談を受けることができる業界初のサービスです。さらに、相談者の必要に応じて、対面カウンセリングを受けることもできます。遠隔と対面の両方の手段を設けることで、相談機会の間口を広げつつ、悩みの内容に合わせた効果的なアドバイスを実施していきます。当サービスでは、大学中退者の就職支援を行うジェイックと、複数の大学に対して中退予防コンサルティング事業を行うNEWVERYが、それぞれの実績とノウハウを生かし、事業開発と運営を展開していきます。 ■背景と展開 昨今の大学中退者数は年間7万人を超えると言われています。中退する理由は、「大学になじめない」、「家庭の経済的事情」、「志望した大学へ入学することに情熱を注ぎ、入学後その熱が冷めてしまった」等があります。そして学生の多くが、キャリア育成等の知見を持つ専門家に相談せずに、大学を辞めることを決めています。ジェイックによる大学中退者の就職活動を支援するサービス“セカンドカレッジ”では、これまで140名を超える大学中退者に携わってきました。“セカンドカレッジ”を受講した学生の中には、「大学中退者の社会における立ち位置」や「今後の人生設計について」の講義を受け、「自身の人生設計をしていく上では大学を卒業したほうが良い」と判断し、復学をする者もいました。しかしながら、対面でのコミュニケーションを苦手とする学生も多く、このような学生が専門家との相談機会を逸することで、適切でないキャリア選択につながっている恐れがあります。このことから、気軽に相談できる機会を提供することで、適切でない大学中退者を減少させることを目指します。NEWVERYは、2009年に日本中退予防研究所を設立し、中退を引き起こす要因の早期発見・早期支援や、本質的な大学教育改革の設計・実行支援を行ってきました。一方で、現在の中退要因分析は、依頼のある個別大学の範囲で、退学済みの学生との接触を通じた原因把握に限られています。当サービスを通じ、中退を検討している学生に直接コンタクトを取ることができることから、現在進行中の学生の実態を大学横断的に把握し、中退の構造要因を精緻に分析していきます。 ■「大学中退相談コンシェルジュ（仮称）」サービス概要

posts.author: youm7.com
posts.title: القضاء الأمريكى يحكم بالسجن 27 عاما على هندى قام بتمويل القاعدة فى اليمن
posts.text:
(أ ف ب) 
حكمت محكمة أمريكية، أمس الاثنين، بالسجن 27 عاما على هندى قدم إلى الولايات المتحدة بهدف الدراسة لانه أرسل أموالا إلى تنظيم القاعدة فى اليمن وتآمر لقتل قاض خلال محاكمته . 
وكان يحيى فاروق محمد (39 عاما) أحد أربعة رجال بينهم شقيقه، أوقفوا فى سبتمبر 2015 واتهموا بتحويل 22 الف دولار الى الداعية الأمريكى أنور العولقى الذى كان يتزعم تنظيم القاعدة فى الجزيرة العربية . 
وسافر محمد واثنان آخران الى اليمن فى 2009 على أمل تسليم المبلغ إلى العولقى الذى كان من أهم الذين عملوا على تجنيد عناصر للقاعدة. لكنهم لم يتمكنوا من لقائه ونقل الآمال طرف ثالث اليه، وبعدما أعتقل فى 2015، حاول محمد استئجار شخص لقتل القاضى الذى ينظر فى قضيته، حسبما ذكرت وزارة العدل الأمريكية . 
وقال المدعى جاستن هردمان انه "هدد سلامة اثنين من مواطنينا هما قاض وموظف قضائي، والآن يحاسب على ذلك "،  وتوجه محمد الى الولايات المتحدة ليدرس فى جامعة اوهايو فى 2002. وقد تزوج من أمريكية فى 2008 . 
وبعد عام على توقيفه، عرض محمد على نزيل معه فى سجن لوكاس كاونتى فى اوهايو 15 الف دولار لخطف وقتل قاضى المنطقة الأمريكية جاك زهارى . 
وقام هذا السجين بتعريف محمد على قاتل كان فى الواقع احد رجال مكتب التحقيقات الفدرالى (اف بى آى). ودفع احد أفراد عائلة محمد رعبونا بلغ الف دولار "للقاتل ".

posts.author: lexpress.fr
posts.title: Cyclisme: un coureur chinois agresse une équipe suisse au Tour de Hainan
posts.text:
Shanghai - Un coureur de l'équipe chinoise Keyi Look, Wang Xin, a été exclu du Tour de Hainan, ainsi que toute sa formation, après qu'il a agressé des membres de l'équipe de Suisse, une altercation qui a nécessité l'intervention de la police. Les organisateurs de cette épreuve sur la petite île dans le sud de la Chine, près du Vietnam, ont indiqué que le coureur et son équipe ne seraient plus jamais invités. 
Une vidéo postée en ligne de l'agression montre un coureur, a priori Wang, en train de tabasser un membre de l'équipe suisse, le jetant à terre et lui donnant des coups de pied dans la tête, avant de s'en prendre à un second. 
Le coureur s'empare alors d'une pompe à vélo dans une des voitures d'assistance, avec visiblement l'intention de s'en servir comme d'une arme, quand trois policiers l'interceptent et lui enlèvent l'objet des mains, au milieu de quelques dizaines de badauds incrédules. 
L'agression s'est produite à la fin de la septième étape, vendredi, du parcours de 166,5 kilomètres entre les villes de Sanya et Wuzhishan. 
Wang Xin reprochait visiblement à une voiture de l'équipe suisse de l'avoir fait tomber durant cette étape. 
La Fédération chinoise de cyclisme (CCA) a ouvert une enquête et pourrait également le sanctionner. 
Cette dernière a souligné n'avoir aucune tolérance pour les " attitudes non civilisées et les comportements violents ", mais a noté que l'incident s'était produit après que la voiture de l'équipe suisse " a eu un contact " avec le coureur, ce qui l'a fait tomber. 
L'ancien coureur Danilo Hondo, manageur de l'équipe suisse, a nié avoir fait tomber Wang: " Nous ne l'avons jamais touché, vous pouvez le voir sur la vidéo de la course ", a-t-il dit à Eurosport. " Il a simplement touché la roue arrière d'un autre coureur et il est tombé. Il était visiblement embarrassé et il a passé sa frustration sur nous ". 
L'équipe Keyi et Wang Xin se sont excusés dans un communiqué sur Weibo, l'équivalent chinois de Twitter, mais ont pointé l'équipe suisse pour avoir fait tomber le coureur avec leur voiture. 
Les organisateurs du Tour de Hainan ont promis de ne jamais plus les accepter au départ. " L'image et la réputation du Tour de Hainan ne peuvent être entachés par un tel comportement ", ont-ils insisté.

posts.title: Obasanjo lands UN job
posts.text:
Former President Olusegun Obasanjo has been appointed into the United Nations (UN) High-Level Advisory Board on Mediation along with 17 other current and former global leaders.

The Secretary-General, Antonio Gutierrez had in September announced the establishment of the board to provide him with advice on mediation initiatives and back specific mediation efforts around the world.


The Board is composed of 18 current and former global leaders, senior officials and renowned experts who bring together an unparalleled range of experience, skills, knowledge and contacts.

The Board is expected to allow the UN to work more effectively with regional organizations, non-governmental groups and others involved in mediation around the world.

According to The Nigerian Tribune,In the announcement of the appointments, the world body described Obasanjo as one of the most distinguished elder statesmen of Africa.

It added:
“He served as President of the Republic of Nigeria from 1999 to 2007, and before that as the Head of the Federal Military Government of Nigeria and Commander-in-Chief of the Nigerian Armed Forces from 1976 to 1979. Over his long career, Mr. Obasanjo has been involved in numerous international mediation efforts, including in Angola, Burundi, Mozambique, Namibia and South Africa.
“In 2008 he was appointed the UN Secretary-General’s Special Envoy on the Great Lakes region.”

posts.text:
De acordo com empresário garanhuense, 52 segmentos da economia local,  receberam  impacto do evento - algo de extrema importância sob a ótica de Freitas. 
A 2º Vaquejada do Dom Roxão, realizada de 1 a 5 de novembro, no Parque Acauã, em Garanhuns, atraiu turistas de vários estados para assistir a tradicional derrubada de bois, o 1• Leilão Haras Brejo das Flores e, ao final, grandes shows com Luan Santana, Aviões do Forró e Mano Walter. 
De acordo com o empresário Givaldo Calado de Freitas é preciso evidenciar que iniciativas como esta são de extrema importância para Garanhuns, porque movimenta a cidade e bombeia sua economia. 
"Foram 52 segmentos da economia que receberam o impacto dessa promoção, e desse impacto a economia de Garanhuns precisa", comenta o empresário. 
“Quero, aqui, saudar e parabenizar a iniciativa dos empresários garanhuenses, Erlan Bezerra e Elison Bezerra, pela exitosa realização, que contou com excelente organização e gigantesca estrutura, mostrando, sobretudo, a quem veio de outros estados a grandeza do espetáculo e, em especial, o jeito de Garanhuns fazer suas promoções”, comentou Freitas.  
O evento contou, ainda, com premiações de R$ 260 mil. A novidade nesta edição de 2017, foi a realização do 1º Leilão Haras Brejo Das Flores, onde foram ofertados produtos de criação do Haras do Garanhão Dom Roxão Eternalady, vice-líder do Ranking ABQM, categoria Reprodutor de Vaquejada.

posts.author: Seeline
posts.text:
can you try giving her specific things to do even if they don't need doing
eg 'Come on Mummy'
'I'm just getting a coffee. Why don't you go and find x book/yellow teddy/y puzzle and get things ready and I'll be along to play in a minute'
Or I'm just sorting out your brother/sister can you go and find me his red socks etc.
She may then get distracted whilst hunting and give oyu 5 minutes. It will also help her start being a bit more independent.
